lling at absorbing damage while providing crucial utility to the team. His Overcharge mechanic makes him particularly effective at dealing burst damage when the situation demands it.\n\nMaelle\u2019s unique Virtuose Stance system transforms her from a solid attacker into a devastating damage dealer. Mastering her stance transitions is key to unlocking her full potential. This build optimizes Maelle for solo combat situations, maximizing her damage output when fighting alone. Medalum\u2019s scaling with Luck makes it ideal for early game dominance. The weapon\u2019s synergy with Virtuose Stance creates opportunities for massive damage spikes when properly executed. Your primary strategy involves applying Burn through Free Aim shots, then using Swift Stride to instantly enter Virtuose Stance. Once in stance, Percee becomes your primary damage tool, capable of dealing devastating damage to marked enemies. This advanced build leverages Maelle\u2019s counterattack capabilities to maintain constant Virtuose Stance activation. Jarum\u2019s ability to trigger Virtuose Stance on any counterattack makes this build incredibly powerful.",
