        "type": "knowledge",
        "title": "Clair Obscur: Expedition 33 \u2013 Ultimate Verso Build Guide (Best Skills, Weapons, and Strategies)",
        "url": "https://www.keengamer.com/articles/guides/clair-obscur-expedition-33-ultimate-verso-build-guide-best-skills-weapons-and-strategies/",
        "metadata": {
