        "title": "Best Expedition 33 Sciel Build (Support Sciel) \u2013 Clair Obscur",
        "url": "https://hacktheminotaur.com/clair-obscur-expedition-33/best-sciel-build-support-sciel/",
        "metadata": {
          "type": "webpage_metadata",
