        "text": "Register! ... This, alongside Intervention and Delaying Slash makes Sciel BY FAR the best support character in the game. Every setup that does incomprehensible amounts of damage always starts with Sciel.\n\nFortune's Fury is a Skill in Clair Obscur Expedition 33. Skills are unique abilities for the playable Characters of the game; each character consists of a skill tree that requires skill points and other skills to unlock. ... Skill Effect: Targeted ally deals double damage for 1 turn. ... Notes, Tips, and other Trivia for Fortune's Fury Skill go here. Join the page discussion Tired of anon posting? Register! ... This, alongside Intervention and Delaying Slash makes Sciel BY FAR the best support character in the game. Every setup that does incomprehensible amounts of damage always starts with Sciel. ... Surely, if running Cheater, you will lose this buff if used on turn 1. ... I'm guessing \"immediately plays again\" aka second turn will not be affected by this, correct? Cheater + this would be pretty broken i think ...",
