    "text": "Based on the progression plan in your own overview file, I'd say the clearest transition point is **The Reacher / Renoir** \u2014 roughly level 75\u201380. That's where Phase 3 ends and Phase 4 begins, Maelle gets her endgame weapon (Lithum), the endgame team (Maelle/Sciel/Verso) comes fully online, and post-game content unlocks.\n\nBefore that, you're still building toward the team composition rather than optimising within it \u2014 Verso doesn't have Steeled Strike yet, Sciel's Litheson isn't at level 20, Maelle is on Medalum. The Cheater Pictos from Sprong is probably the other key milestone: once Verso has Cheater + Steeled Strike, his damage ceiling changes significantly.\n\nSo I'd put it as: **mid-game ends when you defeat Renoir and Maelle has Lithum**. Everything in Phases 2 and 3 is the bridge.\n\nThat said, this is my interpretation of the structure, not something I've searched. If you want I can look for how the community defines the transition.",
